::Aerotaur/Terrataur::
       He watches the monitor and winces.  He opens a com to Terrataur.  
"Terrataur, I need you to go out side and get Windlord, Quetzalcoatl, and 
Starstomp inhere with one of your tunnels.

       She receives the com.  "Acknowledged."  She digs a tunnel outside to 
the fighting, planting bombs behind her to collapse the tunnel in case of 
invasion.  "Hey!  GET IN HERE!  NOW!"

--part1_d.20ec6ca1.297f78ba_boundary
